"<guibutton>Gleich (=)</guibutton>: Ändert den Ordner im Dateifenster zum "
"Ordner des anderen Dateifensters."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:231
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guibutton>Up Button (..)</guibutton>: changes the panel directory to the "
#| "parent directory."
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Up Button (..)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the "
"parent folder."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Aufwärts (..)</guibutton>: Wechselt zum übergeordneten Ordner im "
"Dateifenster."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:236
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guibutton>Home Button (~)</guibutton>: changes the panel directory to "
#| "the home directory."
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Home Button (~)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the home "
"folder."
