"<guibutton>Persönlicher Ordner (~)</guibutton>: Geht zum Persönlichen Ordner "
"im Dateifenster."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:241
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guibutton>Root Button (/)</guibutton>: changes the panel directory to "
#| "the root directory."
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Root Button (/)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the root "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Basisordner (/)</guibutton>: Geht im Dateifenster zum Basisordner "
"des Dateisystems."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:246
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
